default6.1
default&#xa0; 
defaultThe public were intended to be the beneficiaries of the data but were not often named as the biggest users. This may because of the general barriers to participation outlined above. It may also be connected to where the interest of the public lies. Interviewees pointed out that general ‘engagement’ with local government concerned ‘problems’ or daily matters rather than spending. One Metropolitan Borough Council publishes the number of visits per month to various parts of its website. 
